    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh wait r u saying i shouldn't drink more water?? i thought that was the point. i'm also feeling a bit lightheaded and my stomach is kinda cramping up too. if i just take a slightly higher dose of my lithium tonight i can probably stabilize things and get past this phase faster, right? it's better to just power through it than to miss a dose and mess up my mood.",
